candidate_id.description:

If a person runs for several offices, that person will have separate candidate IDs for each office.

committee_id.description: A unique identifier assigned to each committee or filer registered with the FEC. In general committee id's begin with the letter C which is followed by eight digits.

committee_name.description: The name of the committee. If a committee changes its name,     the most recent name will be shown. Committee names are not unique. Use committee_id     for looking up records.

image_number.description: An unique identifier for each page where the electronic or paper filing is reported.
